                <div class="sms-row"><div class="sms-bd"><div class="sms-top"><b>__SMS_N2__</b><span class="rl">__SMS_RL2__</span><time>__SMS_TM2__</time></div><div class="sms-prev">__SMS_PV2__</div></div></div>
                <div class="sms-row"><div class="sms-bd"><div class="sms-top"><b>__SMS_N3__</b><span class="rl">__SMS_RL3__</span><time>__SMS_TM3__</time></div><div class="sms-prev">__SMS_PV3__</div></div></div>
                <div class="sms-row"><div class="sms-bd"><div class="sms-top"><b>__SMS_N4__</b><span class="rl">__SMS_RL4__</span><time>__SMS_TM4__</time></div><div class="sms-prev">__SMS_PV4__</div></div></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
```
#### C-10 · 语音留言（voice）
> 填写：`__VOICE_DUR__` 时长(如 0:14)、`__VOICE_TRANSCRIPT__` 逐字稿一句，最适合直接用 `opening` 里那句撒娇/求陪伴，是最强搭话钩。波形 `.wave` 不动。
```html
<div class="sec">
          <div class="sh"><div><span class="en">Voice</span><div class="t">__VOICE_TITLE__</div></div><span class="x">__VOICE_DUR__</span></div>
          <div class="voice">
            <div class="play"><svg viewBox="0 0 16 16"><path d="M4 2.5v11l9-5.5z"/></svg></div>
            <div class="wave"><i style="height:7px"></i><i style="height:13px"></i><i style="height:19px"></i><i style="height:11px"></i><i style="height:16px"></i><i style="height:22px"></i><i style="height:10px"></i><i style="height:15px"></i><i style="height:8px"></i><i style="height:18px"></i><i style="height:12px"></i><i style="height:16px"></i><i style="height:9px"></i><i style="height:14px"></i><i style="height:20px"></i><i style="height:11px"></i><i style="height:17px"></i><i style="height:7px"></i></div>
            <div class="duration">__VOICE_DUR__</div>
          </div>
          <div class="transcript">__VOICE_TRANSCRIPT__</div>
        </div>
```
#### C-11 · 新闻卡 / 热搜榜（media，仅公众人物）
> 填写：`__MEDIA_CAT__` 分类标、`__MEDIA_TITLE__` 报道标题、`__MEDIA_BODY__` 摘要一句、`__MEDIA_SRC__` 来源；3 条热搜词 `__RANK_KWx__`+热度。光鲜头条下藏一条只有你能看穿的暗线。前两行 `.hot` 保留。
```html
<div class="sec">
          <div class="sh"><div><span class="en">Media</span><div class="t">__MEDIA_SEC_T__</div></div></div>
          <div class="mini">Article · 报道卡</div>
          <div class="media-card">
            <div class="media-kicker"><span class="cat">__MEDIA_CAT__</span><span class="tm">__MEDIA_TM__</span></div>
            <div class="media-title">__MEDIA_TITLE__</div>
            <div class="media-body">__MEDIA_BODY__</div>
            <div class="media-src"><span class="src-dot"></span>__MEDIA_SRC__</div>
          </div>
          <div class="mini">Rank · 实时热搜</div>
          <div class="rank-row hot"><span class="num">1</span><span class="kw">__RANK_KW1__</span><span class="flame">爆</span></div>
          <div class="rank-row hot"><span class="num">2</span><span class="kw">__RANK_KW2__</span><span class="heat">__RANK_H2__</span></div>
          <div class="rank-row"><span class="num">3</span><span class="kw">__RANK_KW3__</span><span class="heat">__RANK_H3__</span></div>
        </div>
```
#### C-12 · 评论 / 他人评价（comment）
> 填写：3 条（可增减）。头像 class 保留（缺省/`.gray`/`.dark` 三种皮肤）。每条：`__CM_AVx__` 头像 1~3 字、`__CM_NAMEx__` 昵称、`__CM_ROLEx__` 身份小标、`__CM_Px__` 评价一句、`__CM_LIKEx__` 点赞(可留空)。呈现外界印象 vs 真实的落差，勾起"我想认识真的 ta"。
```html
<div class="sec">
          <div class="sh"><div><span class="en">Comments</span><div class="t">__CM_TITLE__</div></div></div>
          <div class="comment-stack">
            <div class="comment"><div class="avatar">__CM_AV1__</div><div><div class="cmeta"><b>__CM_NAME1__</b><span class="rolechip">__CM_ROLE1__</span></div><p>__CM_P1__</p><div class="like">__CM_LIKE1__</div></div></div>
            <div class="comment"><div class="avatar gray">__CM_AV2__</div><div><div class="cmeta"><b>__CM_NAME2__</b><span class="rolechip">__CM_ROLE2__</span></div><p>__CM_P2__</p><div class="like">__CM_LIKE2__</div></div></div>
            <div class="comment"><div class="avatar dark">__CM_AV3__</div><div><div class="cmeta"><b>__CM_NAME3__</b><span class="rolechip">__CM_ROLE3__</span></div><p>__CM_P3__</p></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
```
#### C-13 · 论坛盖楼帖（forum，仅公众人物）
> 填写：`__FR_BOARD__` 板块名、`__FR_TITLE__` 帖子标题、回复/点击数；主楼(op)+2 跟帖，各填 `__FR_NAMEx__` 用户名、楼层、`__FR_TEXTx__` 发言。第 3 楼可用 `.fquote` 引用主楼。头像 class(缺省/`.g`/`.d`)保留。用路人视角制造话题度与神秘感、放大反差。
```html
<div class="sec">
          <div class="sh"><div><span class="en">Forum</span><div class="t">__FR_SEC_T__</div></div><span class="x">__FR_X__</span></div>
          <div class="forum">
            <div class="fhead">
              <div class="fboard">__FR_BOARD__</div>
              <div class="ftitle">__FR_TITLE__</div>
              <div class="fstat"><span data-k="回复">__FR_REPLY__</span><span data-k="点击">__FR_VIEW__</span><span data-k="更新">刚刚</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="fpost op">
              <div class="fav">__FR_AV1__</div>
              <div class="fbd">
                <div class="fmeta"><span class="fname">__FR_NAME1__</span><span class="ftag">楼主</span><span class="ffloor">主楼</span></div>
                <div class="ftext">__FR_TEXT1__</div>
                <div class="ffoot"><span class="up">__FR_UP1__</span><span class="re">回复 __FR_RE1__</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fpost">
              <div class="fav g">__FR_AV2__</div>
              <div class="fbd">
                <div class="fmeta"><span class="fname">__FR_NAME2__</span><span class="ffloor">2L</span></div>
                <div class="ftext">__FR_TEXT2__</div>
                <div class="ffoot"><span class="up">__FR_UP2__</span><span class="re">回复</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="fpost">
              <div class="fav d">__FR_AV3__</div>
              <div class="fbd">
                <div class="fmeta"><span class="fname">__FR_NAME3__</span><span class="ffloor">7L</span></div>
                <div class="fquote"><b>@__FR_NAME1__：</b>__FR_QUOTE__</div>
                <div class="ftext">__FR_TEXT3__</div>
                <div class="ffoot"><span class="up">__FR_UP3__</span><span class="re">回复</span></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
```
#### C-14 · 采访 Q&A（qa）
> 填写：3 组问答（可增减）。`__QA_Qx__` 问题、`__QA_Ax__` 回答，贴 speech_style。最后一问答出私人渴望，制造亲近感。
```html
<div class="sec">
          <div class="sh"><div><span class="en">Interview</span><div class="t">__QA_TITLE__</div></div></div>
          <div class="qa">
            <div class="qa-row"><div class="q"><span class="qmark">Q.</span>__QA_Q1__</div><div class="a">__QA_A1__</div></div>
            <div class="qa-row"><div class="q"><span class="qmark">Q.</span>__QA_Q2__</div><div class="a">__QA_A2__</div></div>
            <div class="qa-row"><div class="q"><span class="qmark">Q.</span>__QA_Q3__</div><div class="a">__QA_A3__</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
```
#### C-15 · 时间线 · 竖向漫游（timeline）
> 填写：4 段（可增减）。每段：`__TL2_DATEx__` 年份+英文阶段标、`__TL2_Tx__` 标题、`__TL2_Xx__` 一句说明。落点停在"现在的 ta 需要什么"，引向当下。
```html
<div class="sec">
          <div class="sh"><div><span class="en">Timeline</span><div class="t">__TL2_TITLE__</div></div></div>
          <div class="tl">
            <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-date">__TL2_DATE1__</div><div class="tl-t">__TL2_T1__</div><div class="tl-x">__TL2_X1__</div></div>
            <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-date">__TL2_DATE2__</div><div class="tl-t">__TL2_T2__</div><div class="tl-x">__TL2_X2__</div></div>
            <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-date">__TL2_DATE3__</div><div class="tl-t">__TL2_T3__</div><div class="tl-x">__TL2_X3__</div></div>
            <div class="tl-row"><div class="tl-date">__TL2_DATE4__</div><div class="tl-t">__TL2_T4__</div><div class="tl-x">__TL2_X4__</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
```
